Print skim objects

Source: R/skim_print.R
print.Rd

Print skim objects

# S3 method for skim_df
print(x, ...)

# S3 method for skim_vector
print(x, ...)

# S3 method for summary_skim_df
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

Either a skim_df, skim_vector or skim_summary object.
...

Further arguments passed to or from other methods.

Methods (by class)

  • skim_df: Prints a skimmed data frame (skim_df from skim())

  • skim_vector: Manages print for skim_vector objects.

  • summary_skim_df: Print method for a summary_skim_df object.
